      <li>170M new jobs vs. 92M displaced <em><a href="https://blog.theinterviewguys.com/the-state-of-ai-in-the-workplace-in-2025/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">(The Interview Guys)</a></em></li>
      <li>39% of job skills changing by 2030 <em><a href="https://quantaintelligence.ai/2025/02/10/technology/ai-job-report-2025-q1?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">(Quanta Intelligence)</a></em></li>
