    <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Nurture Ethical and Human-Centered Creators</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
      As AI becomes more powerful, questions about fairness, transparency, and agency grow more urgent. Learning to critically evaluate AI outputs and embed values in design isn’t optional—it’s foundational.
    </p>
